## English Summary

This project uses dual licensing:

1. **Source Code**: Licensed under MIT License
2. **Data Files** (in `docs/` directory): Licensed under Taiwan Open Government Data License (compatible with CC BY 4.0)

**Data Source**: Directorate-General of Personnel Administration, Executive Yuan, R.O.C.  
**Data License**: https://data.gov.tw/license

When using the data, please provide attribution:
```
Data Source: Directorate-General of Personnel Administration, Executive Yuan, R.O.C.
Licensed under Open Government Data License
License: https://data.gov.tw/license
```
